      map_after_p: 'The building locations of the 4 schools starting in April 2027. They will use the existing buildings of the same-named schools (Tokadai Higashi Elementary/JHS and Tokadai Nishi Elementary/JHS). <strong>Schools are divided into "East Group" and "West Group."</strong>',
